This script will build yabridge with 32bit plugin support and yabridgectl
This depends on multilib wine compiled with 32-bit boost and must be installed in /use/bin

Remember that if you update boost you have to update the 32-bit manually
It better to not let that happen by using:

echo "boost" >> /etc/slackpkg/blacklist

# to see if you need to manually update boost
slackpkg show-changelog
